FBIS4-61741 "drsov090_b_94008" FBIS-SOV-94-090 Daily Report 9 May 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Yeltsin Signs Law on Federal Assembly Deputies Yeltsin Signs Law on Federal Assembly Deputies LD0905135894 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 1323 GMT 9 May 94 LD0905135894 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service Russian BFN [Text] Moscow, 9 May (ITAR-TASS) -- Russian President Boris Yeltsin has signed the federal law on "The Status of a Deputy of the Federation Council and the Status of a Deputy of the State Duma of the Federal Assembly of the Russian Federation." This document defines the rights, duties, and responsibilities of Federal Assembly deputies, and stipulates the main legal and social guarantees enabling them to do their work.
